# W3C & WCAG

- `<section>` only when it contains a heading (`h2`–`h6`); otherwise use `<div>`.
- No `role="link"` on `<a>`, no `type="submit"` on anchors, no `role="timer"`.
- `aria-label` on `<div>` requires `role="group"` (or semantic element).
- Touch targets ≥ 44×44px; visible `:focus-visible` ring (emerald `#10b981`).
- Do not nest interactive elements inside `<p>`. Use `<div>` + `<span>` for mixed Link/text.
- Progress bars: `role="progressbar"` + `aria-valuemin/max/now`.
- Numeric labels: `font-feature-settings: "tnum"`.
